{"tid":2059051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕唔好比DNA sample","createTime":"2020-06-10T15:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T15:23:23.000Z","uid":149092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f78a8f3b40896212b1631ef0038ab7b741a87130","tid":2059051,"uid":149092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"上外國網站見到被捕須知教示威者拒絕比DNA sample啲警察<br />\n例如swab你塊面，比杯水你飲<br />\n唔知香港啲狗會唔會都咁做？<br />\n唔知會唔會同政府最近放風想搞DNA庫有關<br />\n手足要小心<br />\n<br />\nDon&rsquo;t give a DNA sample<br />\n<br />\nDuring the arrest, the police may try to obtain your DNA by swabbing your cheek. Do not consent to give a DNA sample, even if the cops make it seem like a standard arrest procedure.<br />\n<br />\nA cheek swab is a common way to obtain DNA, but police have other methods you should watch out for, including offering you water bottles, cigarettes or gum. It&rsquo;s best not to accept anything from the police&mdash;and especially not during an arrest.<br />\n<br />\n醬油：<a href=\"https://lifehacker.com/what-to-do-if-youre-arrested-while-protesting-1843921685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fwhat-to-do-if-youre-arrested-while-protesting-1843921685&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=e8820bda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lifehacker.com/what-to-do-if-youre-arrested-while-protesting-1843921685</a>"},{"pid":"983be7a3bc5e38974f54f40c057505b4c9d1936f","tid":2059051,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697042f2f1f6583ad56a1c12e9de375bebe5c84e","tid":2059051,"uid":6058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"你估班仆街會唔會夾硬來？<br />\n佢要起<br />\n我哋冇得揀<br />\n外國仲要偷偷摸摸去攞<br />\n但香港係光明正大去拎<br />\n佢要拎<br />\n俾佢<br />\n之後再離開香港"},{"pid":"39afe1e426ba2ca5a1c07f7d217dc87da7ffd033","tid":2059051,"uid":266676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"打到你爆晒缸，大把dna 啦"}]}